Inserir no arquivo /etc/apache2/httpd.conf

LoadModule python_module modules/mod_python.so

<Directory /var/www/>
  Options Indexes FollowSymLinks MultiViews
  AllowOverride None
  Order allow,deny
  allow from all
  AddHandler mod_python .py
  PythonHandler mod_python.publisher
  PythonDebug On
</Directory>
